      <hedline>
        <hl1>KASTOR TO RUN BOSTON</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <byline class="print_byline">By FRANK LITSKY</byline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Deena Kastor will run in Boston Marathon (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>The Boston Marathon scored a coup yesterday when it added Deena Kastor, the 33-year-old American who ran the world's fastest time for a woman last year, to its April 16 race, which is six days before the London Marathon. It will be Kastor's Boston debut.</p>
        <p>FRANK LITSKY</p>
      </block>
